{"tid":201992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓太陽節彩排 小朋友全都是這個表情!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-04-15T07:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T17:10:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef04535193b626bc53ac9a44466cc44bed2c0d89","tid":201992,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpR2tFBJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpR2tFBJ.jpg&h=bbb603de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpG6cLHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpG6cLHg.jpg&h=762a91f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小朋友面露笑容。（歐新社）<br />\n2017-04-15  08:43<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓為迎接金日成105歲冥誕、同時也是重大節日太陽節，除了在國際上叫囂示威，國內也緊鑼密鼓地準備慶祝。<br />\n多家外媒拍攝了北韓為太陽節表演活動進行的事前彩排。照片中的小男孩小女孩將在萬景台少年宮登台，他們全穿著相當具有北韓風格的服飾，有人跳舞、有人歌唱。就算是彩排，每個人臉部也都非常用力露出笑容，表現對元首的尊敬與愛戴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2036813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2036813&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=188c5cc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2036813&h=a457048b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2036813</a>"},{"pid":"24ef7d8f24cd908ee931bdda2a7f2a5c3dc2934d","tid":201992,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:20:49.000Z","msg":"大陸果啲又係咁<br />\n共產國家啲品味真係唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e078b8c8f776ccf9b70438c531791641ece208","tid":201992,"uid":69893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\